要人跟住出去"},{"pid":"dd5b5d46aa6bf89a882baa85f3227e61d38fefc4","tid":1509061,"uid":33709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:40:21.000Z","msg":"要散水唔該大家散遠啲 最好叫埋班花生友走<br />\n唔好諗住自己街坊裝 住得近就無事<br />\n班過街老鼠擺明濫捕、見後生就拉 <br />\n俾佢搞你48小時都好麻煩"},{"pid":"d55169b5db4ed0c862825ca913aa82d2370e41eb","tid":1509061,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c97997ba2097d96887b907738f312a106ed13682","tid":1509061,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T17:03:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:44:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"58cd5e675767e13ad1c5c7b86698cbb45e271102","tid":1509061,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:01:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa0f58c8c3b43eeb5190f3c47ed5b07cb0c4719","tid":1509061,"uid":261937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:14:36.000Z","msg":"得罪全世界後生仔女, 有牌黑社會仲有咩前途?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc2d7bb232b881ace463be4b954b81b02d68abc1","tid":1509061,"uid":154865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T03:31:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a7bbe09e7808d2f6d364e88103f0c870e7098121","tid":1509061,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T03:32:28.000Z","msg":"全面升級 全港開花"},{"pid":"6aa31588bae9030559692fed20c990f9008616d6","tid":1509061,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:39:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7efa0fd4405c1dc49821ee45268bf4fee97600b3","tid":1509061,"uid":157808,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T05:58:59.000Z","msg":"支持前線手足做決定<br />\n但琴日睇完深水埗黃大仙live之後有少少野想同大家學術討論一下<br />\n<br />\n首先深水埗，狗隻依家唔係以驅散為目標，好明顯為拘捕做準備，tg都唔放趕你地走<br />\n琴日睇live見到前排狗隻一衝，手足向後退，但後面已經有另一排重裝企左係到，得返兩條橫街俾大家散<br />\n不過跟住就見幾架狗車係橫街駛出黎<br />\n成件事係要圍住手足去捉人<br />\n<br />\n跟住黃大仙，各位街坊好有興緻食完晚飯出街食糖水睇大仙既七色彩雲<br />\nd狗隻淋浴左係彩雲到咁耐都感化唔到佢地<br />\n但其實佢地上裝再衝出黎捉人唔需要好耐時間<br />\n一直係到等大家以為佢地唔做野放下戒心<br />\n跟住就狗衝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今朝再睇埋柒婆講既野，副圖就清楚左<br />\n如果佢地真係想10.1前瓦解個運動<br />\n但又唔答應五大訴求<br />\n咁佢地個算盤應該就係係呢一個月裡面盡量捉晒前線手足<br />\n仲有大約4個禮拜8個週末<br />\n每次捉10個8個<br />\n加埋平日夜晚挑釁下大家圍狗屋<br />\n夾夾埋埋都可以捉成百個手足交差<br />\n諗住洗乾淨個太平地去飲香檳<br />\n<br />\n所以大家不如諗下呢段時間盡量保留實力<br />\n去唔同地方準備物資<br />\n去各大小黨鐵商場諗下戰術<br />\n去春袋到睇下空姐<br />\n人鏈都搞得咁成功<br />\n大家一齊window shopping或者去識空姐空少一定冇問題既<br />\n<br />\n到月中月尾先再戰<br />\n到時佢地一定急過我地<br />\n犯既錯可能更多<br />\n<br />\n但當然如果佢地用呢段時間黎搜捕手足就另計<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊下點部署好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可 </span></span>"},{"pid":"f259d615b1abed895c2392aa1e0e92c94ba2450d","tid":1509061,"uid":281342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:02:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YB8MzXc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYB8MzXc.jpg&h=784ee190&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JZrKmCd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJZrKmCd.jpg&h=5f5a5766&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CV1a1Cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCV1a1Cd.jpg&h=eb50c548&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/24e0EoT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F24e0EoT.jpg&h=6a789cd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rfNhGCd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrfNhGCd.jpg&h=0c34587a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a9df69880173c4e08db1f914a0171af76238af6","tid":1509061,"